				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-Cao-M%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%A1c-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-x%C3%A3-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-qu%E1%BA%ADn-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n/poem-OHMF-SMTUy8SSs3daJWY0Q">Chân Định huyện, Cao Mại tổng, Bác Trạch xã Phạm quận công bi văn - 真定縣高邁總博澤社范郡公碑文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A5u-k%C3%AA/poem-R0s9NdltdbAGnZNPrsk8pw">Đấu kê - 鬥雞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90oan-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-HBNcmQVGk-O6qH18P8dJoA">Đoan dương - 端陽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A1-Tr%E1%BA%A1c/Kh%E1%BA%A5p-Ng%C6%B0-H%E1%BA%A3i/poem-pxFrBfVzs5nGv9pOp4KKIQ">Khấp Ngư Hải - 泣魚海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A1-Tr%E1%BA%A1c/author-_QnQS6Qw4ar7fP54m2Y1tA">Dương Bá Trạc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ly-s%C6%A1n/poem-qiuEi_9fAjeYIpH8p4ty4g">Ly sơn - 驪山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%E1%BA%BF-vi%C3%AAn/poem-fyhwI7nxI2KiuZrAkVkj9Q">Phế viên - 廢園</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ch%E1%BB%89-h%E1%BB%93i-qu%E1%BB%91c-h%E1%BB%B7-ph%C3%BA-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-phong-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-r3T21pcRqFnK42dMnWo1ng">Phụng chỉ hồi quốc hỷ phú thuật hoài cổ phong nhị thập vận - 奉旨回國喜賦述懷古風二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author--2pwC2FLqv5BAX5uZnZLaA">Phan Huy Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-d0BbbnD7CNSb05WX4DsuXA">Thiếu niên hành kỳ 4 - 少年行其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi-Ph%C3%BAng-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-quan-T%C3%A0o-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-ho%E1%BA%A1-m%C3%A3-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-4yoEq5GRUdDDRggLQ7AyqA">Vi Phúng lục sự trạch quan Tào tướng quân hoạ mã đồ - 韋諷錄事宅觀曹將軍畫馬圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i-t%C3%A1c/poem-kse8kfaCIbQYbXultvHmSA">Xuất tái tác - 出塞作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br></div>	</div>
